com.example.rocketapp.controller

Class UserManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.rocketapp.controller.UserManager
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MockUserManager

    public class UserManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Handles creating, retrieving, and modifying users as well as signing in to firestore. Singleton with static methods for convenience.
